urse, that it would be that big. But of course we also worked really hard for that.\" Since the formation of their YouTube channel, the identity of \"Future House Music\" included an addition of a record label (formed in 2016), merchandises and international events.<ref name=\"TIOH\"/><ref name=\"SKD\">{{Cite web |url=https://www.skiddle.com/news/all/Future-House-Music-heads-to-Leeds-/31277/ |title=Future House Music heads to Leeds |website=Skiddle.com  |access-date=26 January 2018}}</ref>\n\n==Artists==\n{{columns-list|colwidth=15em|style=width: 900px;|\n*Andy Bianchini<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*Asketa\n*AWR<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*Bobby Rock<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*Bougenvilla<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*[[Brooks (DJ)|Brooks]]<ref name=\"DJM\"/>\n*Dastic\n*DLMT<ref name=\"YEM\">{{Cite web |url=http://www.youredm.com/2016/10/26/dlmt-rawd-ft-stevyn-forbidden-dreams-future-house-music-free-dl/ |title=DLMT & RAWD ft. Stevyn \u2013 Forbidden Dreams [Future House Music] [Free DL] |date=26 October 2016 |website=Your EDM  |access-date=26 January 2018}}</ref>\n*[[D-Wayne]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.broadwayworld.com/bwwmusic/article/D-Wayne-Talks-to-Everybody-in-New-Track-Trippin-20171206 |title=D-Wayne Talks to Everybody in New Track 'Trippin' |last=Desk |first=BWW News  |access-date=26 January 2018}}</ref>\n*Ellis<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*FaderX\n*Higher Self<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*Holl & Rush<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.traxsource.com/title/861558/another-day/ |title=Holl & Rush, Jordan Jay \u2013 Another Day |date=11 September 2017  |website=traxsource  |access-date=10 February 2018}}</ref>\n*Jelle Slump<ref name=\"DJM\"/>\n*Jonas Aden<ref name=\"DJM\"/>\n*Junior J<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*Lenx & Denx<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*Maiki Vanics<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*Matt Nash<ref name=\"BP\"/>\n*[[Merk & Kremont]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://thegroovecartel.com/2017/12/30/merk-kremont-turn-it-around/ |title=Merk & Kremont finally release \"Turn It Around\" on Future House Music |date=30 December 2017 |webs